# Normalize line endings. The repo's working copy is LF throughout, so store and
# check out LF everywhere rather than letting core.autocrlf on Windows rewrite every
# file (which is what produces the "LF will be replaced by CRLF" churn). Nothing here
# needs CRLF: .NET, Node and PowerShell 7 all read LF fine on Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary — never touch these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.dll binary
*.nupkg binary
*.snupkg binary

